{% comment %}
  StyleHub Miami — FAQ Page
  Design: DM Sans, Navy #1A1A2E, Red #E53E3E
{% endcomment %}

<div class="faq-page page-width">

  <div class="faq-hero">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p>Quick answers to the most common questions about shopping with StyleHub Miami.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-container">

    <details class="faq-item" open>
      <summary>What is StyleHub Miami?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>StyleHub Miami is an online store based in Miami, FL that curates the best deals across fashion, beauty, electronics, home goods, and sports products. We partner with trusted retailers to bring you authentic products at great prices, all in one convenient place.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Are your products authentic?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Yes. All products are sourced from authorized retailers and verified suppliers. We do not sell counterfeit or knockoff products.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How long does shipping take?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Most domestic US orders arrive within 5–15 business days after processing (1–3 business days). Some items may ship from international partners and take 10–25 business days. Estimated delivery is shown on each product page.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How much does shipping cost?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Shipping costs vary based on item weight and your location. Many items qualify for free shipping — look for the "Free Shipping" badge. Final shipping costs are calculated at checkout.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>What payment methods do you accept?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We accept Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover, Shop Pay, Apple Pay, Google Pay, and PayPal. All transactions are encrypted and processed securely through Shopify Payments.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can I return an item?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Yes. We offer a 30-day return window from delivery date for most products. Items must be unused and in original packaging. Contact <b>support@stylehubmiami.com</b> with your order number to start a return. See our <a href="/policies/refund-policy">Return Policy</a> for full details.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How do I track my order?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Visit our <a href="/pages/tracking">Track My Order</a> page and enter your order number. You'll also receive tracking updates via email once your order ships.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can I cancel or change my order?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>You can request changes within 2 hours of placing your order by emailing support. Once processing begins, modifications are no longer possible, but you can return the item after delivery.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Do you ship internationally?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We primarily ship within the United States. International shipping may be available for select products. Contact support for specific availability.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How do I contact customer support?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Email us at <b>support@stylehubmiami.com</b> or visit our <a href="/pages/contact">Contact page</a>. Our team responds within 24 hours, Monday through Friday, 9 AM – 6 PM EST.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Why did the price change on a product I was viewing?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Our prices reflect real-time market conditions. Prices may fluctuate based on supplier costs and demand. The price shown at checkout is the price you pay. We recommend completing your purchase promptly when you find a deal you like.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>My item arrived damaged. What should I do?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We're sorry to hear that. Please contact us within 48 hours of delivery with photos of the damage and your order number at <b>support@stylehubmiami.com</b>. We'll arrange a replacement or full refund including return shipping at no cost to you.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

  </div>

  <div class="faq-cta">
    <p>Didn't find your answer?</p>
    <div class="faq-cta-links">
      <a href="/pages/help-center" class="faq-btn faq-btn--primary">Visit Help Center</a>
      <a href="/pages/contact" class="faq-btn faq-btn--outline">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<style>
.faq-page { padding:40px 0 60px; max-width:750px; margin:0 auto; font-family:'DM Sans',system-ui,sans-serif; }
.faq-hero { text-align:center; margin-bottom:40px; }
.faq-hero h1 { font-size:32px; font-weight:700; color:#1A1A2E; margin:0 0 8px; }
.faq-hero p { color:#718096; font-size:15px; margin:0; }
.faq-container { margin-bottom:40px; }
.faq-item { border:1px solid #E2E8F0; border-radius:10px; margin-bottom:8px; overflow:hidden; }
.faq-item summary { padding:16px 20px; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#1A1A2E; cursor:pointer; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; transition:background .15s; }
.faq-item summary:hover { background:#F7FAFC; }
.faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display:none; }
.faq-item summary::after { content:'+'; font-size:20px; color:#A0AEC0; flex-shrink:0; margin-left:12px; }
.faq-item[open] summary::after { content:'−'; color:#E53E3E; }
.faq-item[open] summary { background:#F7FAFC; border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0; }
.faq-answer { padding:16px 20px; font-size:14px; color:#4A5568; line-height:1.7; }
.faq-answer p { margin:0; }
.faq-answer a { color:#E53E3E; text-decoration:none; font-weight:500; }
.faq-answer a:hover { text-decoration:underline; }
.faq-cta { text-align:center; background:#F7FAFC; border-radius:16px; padding:32px; border:1px solid #E2E8F0; }
.faq-cta p { font-size:15px; color:#4A5568; margin:0 0 16px; font-weight:600; }
.faq-cta-links { display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:center; }
.faq-btn { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; padding:11px 24px; border-radius:10px; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; transition:all .15s; }
.faq-btn--primary { background:#E53E3E; color:#fff; }
.faq-btn--primary:hover { background:#C53030; }
.faq-btn--outline { background:#fff; color:#1A1A2E; border:2px solid #E2E8F0; }
.faq-btn--outline:hover { border-color:#1A1A2E; }
@media(max-width:480px) {
  .faq-page { padding:24px 16px 40px; }
  .faq-hero h1 { font-size:24px; }
  .faq-cta-links { flex-direction:column; align-items:center; }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "FAQ Page",
  "tag": "section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "FAQ Page" }]
}
{% endschema %}
